imdb.plot outline: Real Houses Of - invites you into some of the most incredible homes in North America. You won't find "cookie cutter" here. These fabulous spaces are one-of-a-kind, custom-designed to fit the needs and lifestyles of their remarkable owners. From historic east coast manors to ultra-modern Pacific pads, these Real Houses push wow factor to the max. With luxurious bedrooms, resort-worthy pools, spectacular bathrooms, million-dollar views and kitchens hot enough to make a French chef swoon - this series is guaranteed to astonish and inspire.
